---
// How‑it‑works section – no props
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Heading -->
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-fg sm:text-5xl">
        From Idea → Tee in 3 Steps
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium text-fg/70">
        Upload artwork, add your link, and we handle the rest—lab‑tested QR codes printed and shipped within 48&nbsp;hours.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps grid -->
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
      <ol class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3 list-decimal marker:text-primary marker:font-bold marker:text-xl pl-6">
        <!-- Step 1: Design -->
        <li class="flex flex-col">
          <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold text-fg">
            <div class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/90">
              <!-- Pencil icon -->
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-bg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.862 3.487a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.182 3.182L7.5 19.213 3 21l1.787-4.5 12.075-12.013Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            Design
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base text-fg/70">
            <p class="flex-auto">
              Upload a PNG, JPG, or SVG—or start from one of our customizable templates in the live editor.
            </p>
          </dd>
        </li>

        <!-- Step 2: Link -->
        <li class="flex flex-col">
          <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold text-fg">
            <div class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/90">
              <!-- QR icon -->
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-bg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 4.5h6v6h-6v-6Zm9 0h6v4.5h-6V4.5Zm0 7.5h4.5v6h-4.5v-6Zm-9 4.5h6v6h-6v-6Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            Add Your Link
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base text-fg/70">
            <p class="flex-auto">
              Drop in any URL—portfolio, playlist, storefront—and we generate a high‑contrast QR code that never stops scanning.
            </p>
          </dd>
        </li>

        <!-- Step 3: Print & Ship -->
        <li class="flex flex-col">
          <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold text-fg">
            <div class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/90">
              <!-- Truck icon -->
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-bg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 13.5V6.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 4.5h9a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25v12a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75h-1.06a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.38 0H9.44a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.38 0H3a.75.75 0 0 1-.75-.75v-2.25H2.25Zm18-3V17.25a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75h-1.06a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.38 0H12.75V10.5h4.287a.75.75 0 0 1 .53.22l2.933 2.93ZM6.75 19.5a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Zm10.5 0a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            Print & Ship
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base text-fg/70">
            <p class="flex-auto">
              Approve the live preview and relax—we print with solvent‑resistant inks, test every QR, and dispatch worldwide within 48&nbsp;h.
            </p>
          </dd>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a
          href="#editor"
          class="inline-block rounded-xl bg-primary text-bg px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold shadow-lg hover:bg-primary/80 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-primary transition-colors duration-200">
          Start Designing
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
